  1. Chhong2-se2 ki3 16:1-7. 21:8-21. 
  Khi3 oh8 Sat-lai7 ka7 i ang A-pek-lan5 tau3 soan2 se3-i5. Hit-si5 i si7 chiong lu2-pi7 Ha7-kah, hou7 i kap i e5 tiong7-hu thong-pang5, kau3-boe2 loan7 kau3 tioh8 koaN2 chhut-khi3. M7-na7 koaN2 se3-i5-a2, lian7 kiaN2 ia7 m7-tihN8, koh hit e5 koaN2-hoat si7 chin chan5-jim2. A-pek-lan5 ke-hoe2 hiah toa7, be7 chhut-tit chit8 chiah iuN5, chit8 chiah lu5 hou7 in. Chiau3 Chhong3-se3-ki3 21:I sou2-ki3. 
  “A-pek-liap8-han2 cha2-cha2 khi2-lai5, theh8 piaN2 kap chit8 phoe5-te7 e5 chui2 hou7 Ha7-kah; he7 ti7 i e5 keng-thau5 teng2; lian5 gin2-na2 soa3 kah i khi3; i chiu7 khi3, kau3 Piat8-si7-pa e5 khong3-ia2 chiu7 kiaN5 bo5 lou7.” Chui2 chiah8 liau2 Ha7-kah chiong kiaN2 khng3 tiam3 chhiu7 kha, put-jim2 khoaN3 kiaN2 go7 si2, chhui3-ta si2, sou2-i2 li7 hng7-hng7 pang3-siaN thi5-khau3 i e5 phaiN2-mia7. Tng I2-sit8-ma2-li7 boe7 chhut-si3 e5 si5 chiu7 hou7 chu2-bo2 phaiN2 khoan2-thai7. Chhong3 16:6 sia2 kong2.
  “Sat-lai7 khou2-chhou2 i, i chiu7 tui3 Sat-lai7 e5 bin7-cheng5 to5-chau2.” Ui7 chit e5 su7 A-pek-lan5 kap Sat-lai7 ti7 ka-teng5 u7 put-tng7 e5 hong-pho, thak8 Chhong3 16:4-6 chiu7 chai. Ha7-kah se3-i5-a2 u7 sin chiu7 siu7 tek-thiong2 khoaN3-khin chu2-bu2, oan-ke kau3 ke-kau2 to bo5 peng5-an. Sat-lai7 khau3-loa7 A-pek-lan5. A-pek-lan5 be7 jim2 tit ka-teng5 put-si5 loan7, chiah tui3 Sat-lai7 kong2 “Lu2-pi7 ti7 li2 e5 chhiu2, li2 thang sui5-i3 khoan2-thai7 i”. In-ui7 Sat-lai7 gia5 Ia5-ho5-hoa lai5 hiap8-che3 pek i e5 tiong7-hu, Sat-lai7 kong2 “Goan7 Ia5-ho5-hoa ti7 li2 goa2 e5 tiong-kan phoaN3-toan3”. Sat-lai7 chin-chiaN3 theng2 i e5 toa7-bou2 e5 chhu5-ui. Toa7 khou2-tok8 ji5 tek8 khou2-tok8. Kau3-boe2 Ha7-kah khoaN3-phoa3, ang-sai3 kah be7 choe3 chu2, theng2 toa7-bou2 khou2-tok8--i. Put-tek-i2 tioh8 chau2, siuN7 beh si2, heng7-gu7 thiN-sai3 chhut-hian7 kio3 i to3 lai5. Chong2-si7 kau3-boe2 kiaN2 chhut-si3 to chap8-goa7 hoe3 lah, ia7-si7 nge7-nge7 koh koaN2 chhut-khi3. Bo5 pun kau3 chit8-te3 oaN2, chit8-siang ti7, khang-chhiu2 koaN2 chhut-khi3. An2-ni lang5 na7 ai3 long7-phoa3 ka-teng5 e5 te7 it hong-hoat tioh8 chhui-chian3 se3-i5 hou7 ang-sai3. 
  Tui3-ti7 A-pek-lan5 kap Ha7-kah thong-pang5 e5 su7 Seng3-keng ka7 lan2 kong2 saN-hang7 tai7-chi3. 
