  2. Chhong3 25:28. 27:1-8. 
  Oh8 I2-sat kap Li7-pek-ka in ang-a2-bou2. SeN nng7 e5 kiaN2 chit8 e5 I2-so3, chit8 e5 Nga2-kok. Lau7-pe7 thiaN3 toa7-kiaN2 I2-so3; in-ui7 i siuN7 kong2 chit e5 e7 khi3 phah-lah8 choe3 ho2 chhai3 thang hou7 i phoe3 sio-chiu2. Lau7-bo2 thiaN3 Nga2-kok, in-ui7 i siuN7 chit e5 khah koai, khah u7 oe7 kong2, e7 pang-chan7 i choe3 ke-lai7 e5 kang tiaN5. An2-ni chit8 lang5 phian-ai3 chit8 e5. Lan7-pe7 kap toa7-kiaN2 su-iok beh ka7 i chiok-hok. Lau7-bo2 ka3 kiaN2 kong2 peh8-chhat8, pang-chan7 i phian3 lau7-pe7. Hai7 tit ke-lai7 loan7 chhau-chhau, hiam2-hiam2 chiu7 jia2-chhut kut-jiok8 hiaN-ti7 sio chan5-sat. Ka-chai3 Nga2-kok chau2 tit li7. Na7-ai3 ke-teng5 loan7, chiu7 ang-bou2 toa7-se3-sim koh phian-ai3 kiaN2-ji5, long7 kiaN2-ji5 sio-cheN ke-hoe2, an2-ni iu5-goan5 chin khoai3-phoa3. Ia7 m7-si7 bo5 po3, Nga2-kok phian3 in lau7-pe7, kau3 ni5-lau7 ia7-si7 hou7 in kiaN2 phian3. I e5 kiaN2 ia7-si7 hiaN-ti7-a2 sio hai7. 
