  5. Sat-bo2-ni2 ha7 11:2-27. 
  Oh8 Tai7-pit8 e5 sia5-loan5, tham Ou-li7-a e5 bou2 Poat8-si7-pa. Tai7-pit8 kiaN5-iu5 ti7 ong5-kiong e5 liang5-tai5-teng2, bo5 tiuN-ti5 khoaN3 tioh8 chit8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 teh se2-ek8, iong5-mau7 chin sui2. An2-ni u7 choe7 a2-bo5? Goa2 siuN7 bo5. Bo5 tiuN-ti5 khoaN3 kui2-na7 e5 hu7-jin5 lang5 long2 chin-sui2, long2 chhiah-sin lou7-the2 teh se2-ek8, un2-tang3 chin ho2 khoaN3. Thang khia7 hia khoaN3 a2-bo5? Tu5 khoaN3 ka-ti7 e5 XX i2-goa7, goa2 siuN7 choat8-tui3 m7-thang. Siat-su2 bo5 tiuN-ti5 hou7 li2 khoaN3 tioh8; goa2 siuN7 lan2 tioh8 kin2 oat-chau2 m7-thang koh khoaN3. In-ui7 lang5 loan2-jiok8 kiaN liau2 tiaN7 tiam3 hia khoaN3 sim-lai7 e7 seN-khi2 sia5-liam7. Tai7-pit8 khoaN3 liau2 be7 soah tit, soa3 chhe-lang5 tham3-thiaN hit e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 si7 chi7-chui7? Ti7-chia i2-keng chho3-gou7. Hit e5 lang5 si7 chi7-chui7 eng3-kai kap Tai7-pit8 bo5 kan-siap8. Ho5-pit tham3-thiaN? Ki3-jian5 chai si7 Ou-li7-a e5 bou2, an2-ni si7 iu2 hu chi hu7. Si7 u7 ang e5 cha-bou2-lang5, koh si7 ka-ti7 e5 pou7-ha7 e5 bou2, chai liau2 ka7 Ou-li7-a tau3 hoaN-hi2 chiu7 ho2. M7-bian2 chhe lang5 khi3 chiong hu7-jin5-lang5 chiap lai5. Hu7-jin5-lang5 siu7 tiau3 iat-kian3 tai7-ong5 che si7 chin eng5-kng. Chu7-jian5 m7-kaN2 gek8-chi2 chiu7 lai5. Lai5, su3-iat ka7 i bian2-le7, in-ui7 si7 ka-ti7 e5 pou7-ha7 e5 chhe-chu2. An2-choaN2 tioh8 chai i e5 XX tu2-a2 chheng-khi3. Ti7 chia Tai7-pit8 chin kai-si2. Chhia loh8-kia7 se3-bin7 oh tong3 lah, kau3-boe2 chu7-jian5 peng2-chhia. Tang5-pang5 lah, u7 sin-in7 lah. Kau3-chia hoan2-hoe2 iau2 si7 tai7-tiong7-hu. Ho5-pit ka-ti7 thau-chiah8, ou-kau2 thau-chiah8, chiah kio3 peh8-kau2 to3 lai5 siu7 choe7. Tu2-tioh8 Ou-li7-a iu7 gong7-tiong, m7 to3-khi3 ti3 Ou-soan-bou7. Goan7 tiam3 ong5-kiong ku jim5-chiN5-kha. Che-iuN7 e5 chin7-tiong eng3-kai tioh8 ki3 tai7-kong chit8-chhu3, toa7-toa7 ka-chiong2. Sim2-mih8 Tai7-pit8 chiah soa3 it-put-chok ji7-put-hiu. Chiam3-bou2 toat8-chhe, soa3 eng7 leng2-to sat-jin5 ke3, pek Ou-li7-a ham7-tin7 cho7-si7 put-kiu3. 
  Chit khoan2-su7 u7 po3 a2-bo5? U7. I e5 kiaN2 Am3-lun3 kan-im5 sio2-moai7 ThaN-ma2. Ap-sa-liong5 ia7-si7 i e5 kiaN2 po3-oan thai5-si2 hiaN-ti7 Am3-lun3 liau2-au7 chiu7 to5-chau2. Au7-lai5 bou5-hoan2, hiam2-hiam2 pek-si2 lau7-pe7 Tai7-pit8. Pek-tit Tai7-pit8 chau2-thau5 bo5 lou7 thau3-me5 koe3 Khip-lun5-khe, siam2-pi7 ti7 soaN-kan khong3-ia2 lai5 chau2-mia7. Kai-chai3 Tai7-pit8 chiong-lai5 u7 toa7-toa7 chham3-hoe2, tit-tioh8 Ia5-ho5-hoa e5 sia3-bian2. 
  6. Ong5 siong7 11:1-14. 
  Oh8 So2-lo5-bun5 lau7 hoan-tian. Thiong2-ai3 goa7-kok e5 bi2-lu2, u7 hou7 hui 700 e5 long2-si7 kui3-chok8 e5, koh u7 pin3-hui 300 e5, chiaN3-keng, hou7-hui, pin3-hui sng3 kui2 chheng e5 bou2. Chin-si7 kai-si2. Seng3-chheh sia2 “Chiah-e5 lu2-chu2 iu2-hek8 i e5 sim …… khi3 pai3 pat8 e5 Siong7-te3, i e5 sim bo5 sun5-choan5 ng3 Ia5-ho5-hoa i e5 Siong7-te3.” Au7-lai5 ui7-tioh8 hiah-e5 bou2, khi2-bio7 kap Seng3-tian7 saN ng3. Kap hiah-e5 bou2 khi3 sio-hiuN ti7 ngou2-siong7 e5 che3-toaN5. 
  Seng3-keng ki3-kong2 “Lun7 kau3 chiah-e5 liat8-kok, Ia5-ho5-hoa bat hoan-hu3 I2-sek-liat8 lang5 kong2, Lin2 m7-thang khi3 in hia, in ia7 m7-thang lai5 lin2 chia, in-ui7 in oe7 hou7 lin2 e5 sim phian-oai, khi3 toe3 in e5 siong7-te3; chong2-si7 So2-lo5-bun5 loan5-ai3 hiah-e5 cha-bou2-gin2-na2, kap in kiat-hun.”(I Liat-ong5 11:2). Khi2 seng3-tian7 toa7 jiat8-sim, sia2 Si-phian e5 chit8-pou7-hun7, sia2 Chim-gian5, sia2 Nga2-ko, sia2 Thoan5-to7, tu3-su lip8-soat, khong-chian5 choat8-hou7 e5 toa7 ti3-hui7 e5 beng5-kun So2-lo5-bun5 sit-pai7 kok phoa3 ti7 chiah-e5 pai3 ngou2-siong7 e5 cha-bou2-gin2-na2. Ah! Chham-sun, Tai7-pit8, So2-lo5-bun5 sui si7 eng-hiong5, tai7-ti3 ia7 lan5-koe3 bi2-jin5-koan. Chin-chiaN3 tioh8 keng2-kai3-ah lu2-sek. 
  7. Liat8-ong5 siong7 16:29. 22:40. Liat8-ong5 ha7 9:29-37. 
  KhoaN3 I2-sek-liat8 ong5 A-khap chhoa7 Se-tun3 ong5 pai3-put8 lang5 e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 Ia5-sian2-piat. Jia2-chhut Ia5-ho5-hoa e5 siu7-khi3 3 ni5 poaN3 bo5 loh8-hou7 toa7 ki-hng. Goan5-in chiu7-si7 choan5-kok pian3-te7 khi2 put8-bio7. Tui3 Se-tun3 tit8 su-jip8 Ang5-i5, Sai-kong, peh-siN3 thang kong2 choan5-kok ngou2-siong7-kau3 hoa3. Chhut Sian-ti I2-li7-a kap hiah-e5 Sai-kong, Ang5-i5 tau3-hoat. Siong7-te3 khah iaN5, chiah koh sin3-giong2 hok8-heng. Ui7 an2-ni Ia5-sian2-piat tai7-theng2 chhu5-ui, ke-bo2 e7 thi5, beng7-leng7 tui sat I2-li7-a. I2-li7-a chit8-si5 toa7-kiaN, chau2-kau3 bo5 iong5-sin chi te7, soa3 ti7 lo5-tin5 chhiu7-e7 kiu5 si2. Au7-lai5 siat-ke3 hou7 Ong5 chiam3 Na2-pok8 e5 pho5-to5-hng5, eng7 chioh8-thau5 tim3 si2 bu5-kou3 e5 Na2-pok8, choe7-chek teng5-teng5 thah8-thah8, kau3-boe2 A-khap kap A-lan5 ong5 chian3-cheng tin7-bong5. Au7-lai5 Ia5-sian2-piat ti7 se-chng-lau5 siu7 Ia5-hou7 kio3 thai3-kam3 tui3 lau5-teng2 e5 thang-a2 ka7 i chhia loh8 khi3; i e5 huih choaN7 tioh8 chhiuN5-piah, sin-si hou7 lang5 thun2-tah8. Kau3 beh ka7 i tai5 e5 si5 chiah kan-ta chhoe7 tioh8 i e5 thau5-khak, kap kha-te5, kap chhiu2-chiuN2. Ki5-u5 e5 long2 hou7 kau2 thoa khi3 chiah8. I2-sek-liat8 kok tui3 an2-ni toa7 soe-bi5, kau3-boe2 bong5-kok. 
  Teng2-bin7 chit chhit e5 kou3-su7 sit8-chai7 hou7 lan2 chin thang kiaN. Lang5 na7 ai3 chhoe7 si2-lou7, ai3 ka-teng5 phoa3, kok-ka bong5 tioh8 khi3 oh8. Ok iu2 ok-po3, sian7 iu2 sian7-po3, m7-si7 bo5 po3, si7 jit8-chi2 boe7 to3. Lan2 e5 sin3-giong2 kiam2 e7 tat8-tioh8 A-peh-liap8-han2, I2-sat, Nga2-kok. Lan2 e5 eng-hiong5 ti3-sek kiam2 e7 tat8-tioh8 Chham-sun, Tai7-pit8, So2-lo5-bun5; choe3 m7-tioh8 Ia5-ho5-hoa Siong7-te3 to iu5-goan5 khian3-chek bo5 sia3-bian2. Ho5-hong3 li2, kap goa2. Tioh8 sio2-sim keng2-seng2. 
  Chi2-moai7 ah, li2 ai3 koh oh8 a2-bo5? Na7-ai3, khi3 oh8 Na2-pho-lun5 e5 kiau-chhe, chha2-loan7 Na2-pho-lun5 kou3 pan7 cheng3-su7, m7 kap i tam7 ai3-cheng5. Kou3 chian3-cheng, tang-chau2 se-phun, lam5-chun5 pak-be2 , m7 kap i san3-pou7 thiau3-bu2. Loan7 kau3 Na2-pho-lun5 bo5 hoat i ta-oa5. Oh8 Thok-ni2-su-thai3 e5 bou2 tiaN7 loan7 in ang be7 hiau2 ai3-chiN5. Loan7 kau3 Thok-ni2-su-thai3 (XXXXX) chau2 bo5 lou7, au7-lai5 khi3 si2 tiam3 ti7 beh khi3 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2 seng3-te7 sun5-le2 e5 chit8-e5 sio2 iah8-thau5. Oh8 Lim5-kheng2 in bou2 chhiah-te-te, keh8-keh8-jiang2, khi3--tioh8 teh lim te5 lian5 te5-poe to tim3-khi3. Pek tit Lim5-kheng2 tioh8 chhut-khi3 liu5. Oh8 Sou-kek-lah8-ti2 e5 bou2 ka7 tiong7-hu lam5 chui2. Oh8 Iok-han7 oe7-su-le2 e5 bou2 bu5-ko3 tiong7-hu tho2 cha-bou2 thau seN-kiaN2. Be7-bai2 ou3; poh-kaN2 si7 chhoa7 tioh8 chhiah cha-bou2, in ang chiah e7 long2 choe3 se3-kai3 e5 ui2-jin5 ia7 bo5 tek-khak. Li2 khoaN3 i2-siong7 e5 le7 kiam2 m7-si7 long2 an2-ni? Lang5 kong2 hou7 chhiah bou2 ka3 chit8-pai2, pi2 hou7 pat8 lang5 ka3 saN-pai2 khah u7 kong-hau7. An2-ni chhoa7 tioh8 chhiah bou2 e5 lang5 bo5 tek-khak si7 bai2. Tan7-si7, mai3-tit khah ho2. 
  TaN chhin-ai3 e5 chi2-moai7, lau2-sit8 kong2 i2-siong7 chiah-e5 bo5 kou3 tiong7-hu e5 keng-che3, bin7-phoe5, kiuh-kiuh-jiong2 ngauh8-ngauh8-liam7-bo5 soah e5 su7, un2-tang3 e7 chiong tiN-bit8 e5 ka-teng5 long7 kau3 na2-chun2 oah8-te7-gek8 e5 khou2-chham2. 
  Ia7 hiaN-ti7, lang5 ti7 se3-kan na7 be7-tit chiong i e5 ka-teng5 choe3 i cheng-sin5-tek un-loan2 in-ai3 an-hioh e5 sou2-chai7. Tioh8 koh-khi3 chin5-lau5 chhou2-koan2, ang5-teng lek8-chiu2, hoa-ke liu2-hang7 lai5 chhoe7 hoan-lok8 an-ui3 e5 lang5 sit8-chai7 chhi-chham2 ah! 
  But8-lun7 ti7 chong-kau3 sim-leng5-siong7 e5 an-ui3 si7 tui3 Siong7-te3 lai5 tit-tioh8. Na7-si7 Jiok8-the2-siong7 cheng-sin5 e5 an-ui3, hiat-kak8 ka-teng5, kong2 ti7 pat8-ui7 iau2 u7 pi2 ka-teng5 khah ho2 e5 sou2-chai7. Ti7 se3-kan iau2 u7 pi2 pe7 bu2 iau2 khah u7 thang chun-keng3, iau2 u7 lang5 pi2 kut-jiok8 e5 hiaN-ti7 khah chhin, iau2 u7 lang5 pi2 ka-ti7 e5 ang-bou2 khah saN-thiaN3, chit e5 lang5 e5 seng-oah8 un2-tang3 chin bo5 chu7-jian5. Eng3-kai si7 seng hau3-keng3 pe7-bo2, seng kut-jiok8 hiaN-ti7 saN-chhin, seng ang-bou2 saN-thiaN3, au7-lai5 tui3 kin7 kau3-hng7, thiaN3 chhu3-piN soa3 kau3 thiaN3 cheng3-lang5, an2-ni chiah be7 si7 hui, thau5-boe2 tian-to3. 
